sources.title: La Soga (Free Full Movie) Crime Drama
sources.description:
Based on true events in the Dominican Republic, one brave cop revolts against his country’s government, risking everything to avenge his father’s death. La Soga is a story of redemption in the midst of brutality and political corruption.

Spanish/English subtitles

Director: Josh Crook
2009
Stars: Manny Perez, Denise Quiñones, Juan Fernández, Margo Martindale, Paul Calderon
